Step to Stl File Conversion Code Steps :

1.Install python software.
2.Open command prompt
3.Install necessary libraires such as cadquery , tkinter , trimesh. 
As pip install cadquery
Pip install tkinter
Pip install trimesh
4.In case for any module not found type pip install modulename
5.Change the current working directory to the python directory.
6. Execute command-code on command prompt as cd pythonpath.
7.Next execute command-code as
 python stos.py where stos is our python script name.
8.Browse the step filewhich you want to convert by clicking import button 
Note : one or more files can be selected simaltaneously.
9.Later click on export button and choose file location in which you need the stl file converted.
